Safedrop,is,a,web,based,messaging,tool,that,acts,as,a,secure,alternative,to,email,The,safedrop,API,provides,a,RESTful,interface,for,integrating,the,service,The,API,is,able,to,return,a,list,of,safedrops,create,a,safedrop,show,or,update,a,safedrop,manage,a,safedrop,s,recipients,manage,a,safedrop,s,files,or,send,a,safedrop,to,all,recipients